parts.text: Thank you for reaching out. I understand you haven't received your message yet. Unfortunately, as a virtual assistant, I don't have the ability to track or deliver text messages. I'm designed to assist with a wide range of tasks, but accessing or managing external communication systems, including text messaging, is beyond my capabilities. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
Ok when massege be received I'll be reply of Y

Okay, I'll be standing by. Once you receive your message and have a reply, feel free to reach out to me again and type "Y". I'll be here to assist you. In the meantime, is there anything else I can help you with today?
